Description: GNY DNS challenge server
 GNY is a FastAPI-based server that manages DNS TXT records for ACME
 dns-01 certificate challenges. It is designed to be used as a hook
 target for certbot or any ACME client when automating TLS certificate
 issuance and renewal.
